# Optional — only needed if you want to run the eval CLI scripts (evals/*.py).
# The Streamlit app itself does NOT read keys from this file; it asks for your
# key in the sidebar at http://localhost:8501.
#
# Copy this file to .env and uncomment the keys you actually use.

